Name: Al Faisaliah Tower
Description: The Al Faisaliah Tower is an iconic skyscraper located in the heart of Riyadh, Saudi Arabia. Standing at over 270 meters tall, it is one of the tallest buildings in the city. Completed in 2000, the tower's modern, spherical design features a 5-star hotel, luxury residences, offices, and a public observation deck at the top, offering panoramic views of Riyadh. The Al Faisaliah Tower is a prominent landmark that has become a symbol of Saudi Arabia's economic and architectural progress.
